id: monica-gitleaks-node24
title: Upgrade Gitleaks action to Node 24 generation
description: Replace gitleaks/gitleaks-action@v2 after merged-head security workflow emitted the GitHub runner Node 20 deprecation warning.
type: Chore
status: in_progress
priority: 1
tags[4]: ci,github-actions,gitleaks,security
created_at: "2026-07-16T17:25:17.411Z"
updated_at: "2026-07-16T17:25:33.368Z"
deadline: "2026-07-18T17:25:17.411Z"
assignee: codex-root
author: codex-root
estimated_minutes: 45
acceptance_criteria: Security workflow uses Gitleaks action v3; secret scan and repository history scan pass; merged master run has no Gitleaks Node 20 deprecation warning
definition_of_ready: Merged-head run 29519584624 identifies the exact action and upstream v3 release is confirmed.
goal: trusted-monica-cli
objective: remove-node20-action-warning
value: Keep secret scanning on a supported action runtime
impact: Avoid future workflow breakage when GitHub stops forcing Node 20 actions onto Node 24
outcome: Clean secret-scan job on the current Gitleaks action generation
why_now: Master security run reports gitleaks/gitleaks-action@v2 as deprecated
parent: monica-platform
reviewer: unbraind
risk: high
confidence: 100
