comments[2]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T17:25:17.411Z",codex-root,"Discovered after #50 merged: Security run 29519584624 warned that gitleaks/gitleaks-action@v2 targets deprecated Node 20."
  "2026-07-16T17:25:33.367Z",codex-root,"Upstream release evidence: https://github.com/gitleaks/gitleaks-action/releases/tag/v3.0.0; tag v3 resolves to e0c47f4f8be36e29cdc102c57e68cb5cbf0e8d1e."
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T17:25:17.411Z",codex-root,"Upstream latest release is v3.0.0, published 2026-05-30; preserve the existing least-privilege permissions and scan steps."
learnings[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T17:25:17.411Z",codex-root,A green workflow can still contain a future-breaking runtime deprecation; merged-head annotations are part of completion evidence.
